<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sys_script_include"><sys_script_include action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><access>public</access><active>true</active><api_name>global.AccessTesterHelper</api_name><client_callable>false</client_callable><description>This script contains the functions used by access tester application.</description><name>AccessTesterHelper</name><script><![CDATA[var AccessTesterHelper = Class.create();
AccessTesterHelper.prototype = Object.extendsObject(AbstractAjaxProcessor, {
	
    /**
     * This function is used to return the list of tables in the instance after excluding system table
     *
     * @returns {string} - list of tables
     */

    getUserTables: function(field) {
        var property = gs.getProperty('access.test.parameters');
        var mainProperties = JSON.parse(property);
        var excludedTables = (mainProperties.excluded_tables_prefix.toString()).split(',');
        var tableFilter = mainProperties.table_basic_filter.toString();
        var excludeTable = false;
        var tables = [];
        var tableName = '';

        var getTables = new GlideRecord('sys_db_object');
        getTables.addEncodedQuery(tableFilter);
        getTables.query();
        while (getTables.next()) {
            tableName = getTables.getValue('name');
            for (var i = 0; i < excludedTables.length; i++) {
                if (tableName.indexOf(excludedTables[i]) == 0) {
                    excludeTable = true;
                    break;
                }
            }
            if (!excludeTable) {
                tables.push(getTables.getValue(field));
            }
            excludeTable = false;
            tableName = '';
        }
        tables.sort();

        return tables.toString();

    },

    type: 'AccessTesterHelper'
});]]></script><sys_class_name>sys_script_include</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>admin</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2019-12-05 08:19:21</sys_created_on><sys_id>7cb0569ddb21001025cf56086896195c</sys_id><sys_mod_count>2</sys_mod_count><sys_name>AccessTesterHelper</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Access Testing" source="85298655db21001025cf560868961960">85298655db21001025cf560868961960</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_scope display_value="Access Testing">85298655db21001025cf560868961960</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_script_include_7cb0569ddb21001025cf56086896195c</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>admin</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2019-12-05 08:19:57</sys_updated_on></sys_script_include></record_update>
